The '''United Tribes Agreement''' formed the [[United Tribes of Kariek]] whose goal was to drive out [[The Warlord]]. The Warlord had ruled their [[Planet/Legends|world]] for more than fifty [[Standard year/Legends|years]] prior to [[Kariek]]'s liberation in [[22 ABY/Legends|22 ABY]] with the support of the [[Empire of the Hand]]. Among its founding members were [[Prince/Legends|Prince]] [[Ha-ran]].

